{"tid":584271,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Duncan桌遊集資最後3日，我地邀請埋佢畫阿源 !","createTime":"2018-03-07T16:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T16:56:15.000Z","uid":46784,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0104c1c38f329d8b8d75233a1c3410ec6f15ec34","tid":584271,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"我地之前已經出過一個Post，話會邀請佢畫有香港特色既圖，而家找數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nvl0fgr7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnvl0fgr7&h=21f05e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/730qw4gz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F730qw4gz&h=a10c7435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係呢到再簡單介紹番個遊戲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3p7fu0lx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3p7fu0lx&h=a790444a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Duncan快跑》係一隻考驗大家創意，同熟識朋友/睇穿人心程度嘅遊戲。每個玩家處心積慮就係為咗集齊最好嘅故事籌碼同埋技能，引到你朋友/陌生人會心一笑之餘，又取巧咁獲得最多嘅分數，絕對唔會破壞友誼（？）<br />\n<br />\n遊戲一共有超過140種不重覆（時間卡、地點卡、動作卡、原因卡、功能卡）並由Duncan獨家繪畫的遊戲卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/alqf3ug7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Falqf3ug7&h=dbb199a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7gdy1exk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7gdy1exk&h=07b4f270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩家可以利用唔同既功能牌去做低其他對手，而且仰要發揮出多年來對朋友的觀察暸解去搶奪分數，最後結果絕對令你意想不到！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 集資去到最後3月10號就會完架啦，想玩既話捉緊機會啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n集資傳送門: <a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/duncanrun?r=5696c72950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeczec.com%2Fprojects%2Fduncanrun%3Fr%3D5696c72950&d=YlEOpzoS0lMG%2FjhymmpRW3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9f98efe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zeczec.com/projects/duncanrun?r=5696c72950</a>"},{"pid":"4afc7fc143db3e16ac1250ea37918666d9727991","tid":584271,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"另外溫馨提示一下嘖嘖上面價錢係台幣黎，我地唔會賣到千幾蚊副bg咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}